---
title: BBQ Veggie Mince & Corn Sloppy Joes with Plant-Based Aioli, Slaw & Fries
description: These divine creations aren't just reserved for American high school cafeterias, they're also great for digging into in the comfort
of your own home. Veggie mince is cooked up with smokey barbecue seasoning for a punch of flavour, while the side of fries and
slaw wrap this delicious dinner up in a neat and tidy bow.
